            "formula": "IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}>4.9, \"Top Performer!\",\n    IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}>4.75, \"Incredible Performance! now let's get to a 4.9 rating or above\",\n        IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}>4.5, \"Great Job! now let's get to a 4.75 or above!\",\n            IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}>4.25, \"Solid Job! How can you improve your rating? Let's get to a 4.5 or above!\",\n                IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}>4, \"You can improve! Schedule a meeting to create a strategy to improve your rating with Maria Eugenia and your PO!\",\n                    IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}>2.99, \"At Singular you are not alone. Let's improve your low rating with a strategy meeting, book a time with Maria Eugenia and your PO!\",\n                        IF({flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8}<=2.99, \"This rating can definitely improve and we are worried its a bit poor! Let's improve your rating with a strategy meeting, book a time with Maria Eugenia!\", \"\"\n                        )\n                    )\n                )\n            )\n        )\n    )\n)\n",
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "flduFHa8ap4B6BOe8"
