            "formula": "IF(\n    {fldZghkRL4J1xU4qa} = \"Lost Satellites (0-20%)\", \"This group represents talents who have drifted far from expectations. Trust has been lost, but with focus and effort, there is potential to realign with the company’s values and rebuild trust.\",\n    IF(\n        {fldZghkRL4J1xU4qa} = \"Comets (21-40%)\", \"You’re on the right path, showing promise and gaining momentum, but still working toward consistency. More reliable performance will solidify your trustworthiness.\",\n        IF(\n            {fldZghkRL4J1xU4qa} = \"Moons (41-60%)\", \"You’re seen as steady and dependable. Like a moon that supports its planet, you provide a reliable presence, but there’s still room to grow into a more influential role.\",\n            IF(\n                {fldZghkRL4J1xU4qa} = \"Planets (61-80%)\", \"You’ve earned a high level of trust, much like planets that support life and stability. Your reliability positively impacts those around you, making you a key player in the team’s success.\",\n                IF(\n                    {fldZghkRL4J1xU4qa} = \"Stars (81-100%)\", \"As a top performer, you are a model of trustworthiness. Like a shining star, you lead by example, inspiring others with your consistent excellence and reliability.\"\n                )\n            )\n        )\n    )\n)",
