              },
              " SF Date\nHere is the list of Stories worked in the sprint\n",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldBifg9QIowMbTfw"
                }
              },
              "\n\nThe structure should be:\n\t1.\tSprint name.\n\t2.\tKey Deliverables grouped by impact.\n\t3.\tPotential KPIs affected.\n\t4.\tAdministrative tasks at the end.\n\nReplace the (Talent or talents: [Talent Name]) with the name of the person who collaborated in the completion of the Key Deliverable.\nThe list of Key Deliverables should be the list of TLDRs, so it can be observed who participated in completing a common goal, and not just a list without grouping.\n\nCreate the Potential KPIs Impacted base on what's worked on the Stories and List it.\n\nTemplate Example:\n\n[Sprint Name]\n\nPotential KPIs Impacted:\n1. [Create list of KPI's]\n\nKey Deliverables:\n1. [Create list of Key Deliverables] (Talent or talents how participated in this Key).\nAdministrative Tasks:\n\t1.\t[Scrum Master Name] coordinated sprint activities and ensured smooth collaboration across the teams.\n\t2.\t[Product Owner Name] oversaw product vision alignment and backlog prioritization.\n"
            ]
          },
