        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "\"Generate an executive summary for the Sprint \\\"\" & {fldJI7UdzncMXrgDP} & \"\\\" using the following stories. The response should be client value-focused, using key deliverables in bullet points. Each deliverable should end with the talent name(s) involved in parentheses. Separate administrative tasks (Scrum Master and Product Owner).\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Include these Sprint details at the start:\\n\" &\r\n\"Sprint Name: \" & {fldJI7UdzncMXrgDP} & \"\\n\" &\r\n\"SO Date: \" & {fldZaG3dLRR23DXeK} & \"\\n\" &\r\n\"SF Date: \" & {fldHNreR04hmHzMsG} & \"\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Here is the list of Stories worked in the sprint:\\n\" &\r\n{fldBifg9QIowMbTfw} & \"\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"The structure should be:\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Sprint name.\\n\" &\r\n\"Key Deliverables grouped by impact.\\n\" &\r\n\"Potential KPIs affected.\\n\" &\r\n\"Administrative tasks at the end.\\n\" &\r\n\"Replace the (Talent or talents: [just one name by talent]) with the name of the person who collaborated in the completion of the Key Deliverable.\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"The list of Key Deliverables should be the list of TLDRs, so it can be observed who participated in completing a common goal, and not just a list without grouping.\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Create the Potential KPIs Impacted based on what's worked on the Stories and list it.\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Template Example:\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"[\" & {fldJI7UdzncMXrgDP} & \"]\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Potential KPIs Impacted:\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"[Create list of KPI's]\\n\" &\r\n\"Key Deliverables:\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"[Create list of Key Deliverables] (Talent or talents who participated in this Key, use one name not full names).\\n\" &\r\n\"Administrative Tasks:\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"[Scrum Master Name] coordinated sprint activities and ensured smooth collaboration across the teams.\\n\" &\r\n\"[Product Owner Name] oversaw product vision alignment and backlog prioritization.\"\r\n",
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldJI7UdzncMXrgDP",
              "fldZaG3dLRR23DXeK",
              "fldHNreR04hmHzMsG",
              "fldBifg9QIowMbTfw"
            ],
            "result": {
              "type": "singleLineText"
            }
          },
          "id": "fldiqYnCujFxSMRDP",
          "name": "Singular Stories Sprint Order TLDR AI_prompt"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "\"Summarize the new app features or key results achieved based only on the development and design stories:\\n\\n\" &\r\n\"Stories:\\n\" &\r\n{fldvnBWkiuhGHViii}\r\n",
            "referencedFieldIds": [
