          "id": "fldsfZ9mUbdIXOFXU",
          "name": "is the sps audited?"
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldb8RgHYMm0Po0yP",
              "fldSVT6sjIw46HVBa",
              "fldEcUFyLMvlvvXLX",
              "fldjAmdwUf3VfIcRa",
              "fldClLPYyEPekW69Q",
              "fldVe6L41rzNPvpYe",
              "fldhJ1yeQPZXbVTUW",
              "fld7a8trjAOvIVec9"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are an Agile estimation auditor assisting a software development company that leverages AI to accelerate automation and task execution.\n\nBased on the following input data, produce an audit summary that is clear, professional, and decision-oriented. The output must be in English.\n\nInputs:\n- User Story: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldb8RgHYMm0Po0yP"
                }
              },
              "\n- Acceptance Criteria: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldSVT6sjIw46HVBa"
                }
              },
              "\n- Story Points suggested by the talent: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldEcUFyLMvlvvXLX"
                }
              },
              "\n- AI’s recommended Story Points (based on benchmarks): ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldjAmdwUf3VfIcRa"
                }
              },
              "\n- Public SP benchmarks for similar tasks:  ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldClLPYyEPekW69Q"
                }
              },
              "\n- Breakdown of the work effort:  ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldVe6L41rzNPvpYe"
                }
              },
              "\n- Reference standards for similar tasks:  ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldhJ1yeQPZXbVTUW"
                }
              },
              "\n- AI’s impact on this story (if any):  \n",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld7a8trjAOvIVec9"
                }
              },
              "\nPlease analyze the above and return:\n\n1. **Status**: Choose from:  \n  - Reasonable  \n  - Slightly Over Estimating  \n  - Slightly Under Estimating  \n  - Over Estimating  \n  - Under Estimating\n\n2. **Justification**: A concise but professional explanation of how the talent's SP suggestion compares to the AI recommendation, considering effort breakdown, story scope, acceptance criteria, references, and AI contribution.\n\n3. **Suggested AI SP**: Return the value of ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldjAmdwUf3VfIcRa"
                }
              },
              " as provided.\n\n4. **AI Impact Summary**: Clarify if AI significantly reduces effort or just contributes partially.\n\n5. **Recommendation**: Provide a short, structured recommendation intended for Product Owners or Agile Delivery Managers. Focus on clarity and next steps (e.g., approve, review in refinement, adjust estimation, clarify scope).\n\nFormat your output as follows:\nStatus: [One of the five]\nJustification: [Concise explanation]\nSuggested AI SP: [Number]\nAI Impact Summary: [Short explanation]\nRecommendation: [Structured suggestion for PO/ADM]\n"
            ]
          },
