        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldYUD8OCHeS0QGnt",
              "fldb8RgHYMm0Po0yP",
              "fldSVT6sjIw46HVBa"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a writing quality auditor for user stories in agile product development.\n\nEvaluate the writing quality of the following user story content and return a Justification Texto of ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldYUD8OCHeS0QGnt"
                }
              },
              "\n\nScoring Criteria:\n- Clarity of the role, goal, and benefit in the user story (As a... I want to... so that...).\n- Correct grammar and spelling.\n- Logical sentence flow and structure.\n- Completeness of the story and criteria, avoiding unnecessary verbosity.\n- Consistency in terminology and formatting.\n\nInput:\nUser Story: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldb8RgHYMm0Po0yP"
                }
              },
              "\nAcceptance Criteria:",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldSVT6sjIw46HVBa"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (MANDATORY):\nReturn only a valid Written ai Justification of this Story\n\n\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldu45fYUQYivAd1k",
          "name": "Writing Quality Grade copy 3"
        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "IF({fldPYcenP6kT4WlPM} > 80, \"Excellent\",\r\nIF({fldPYcenP6kT4WlPM} >= 70, \"Good\",\r\nIF({fldPYcenP6kT4WlPM} >= 60, \"Fair\",\r\nIF({fldPYcenP6kT4WlPM} < 60, \"Poor\"))))",
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldPYcenP6kT4WlPM"
            ],
            "result": {
