eptional ability to maintain healthy relationships, being highly reliable in promoting a collaborative and supportive work culture.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: Intimacy is exceptionally high. The talent sets an exceptional standard for commitment to the project and the ability to maintain healthy relationships, creating a deeply connected and highly trustworthy work environment with both the team and the client.\",\n  \"The score is out of range or not a number\"\n)",
