t Owner demonstrates exceptional knowledge and application in managing communication and leadership, being highly reliable in promoting a deeply connected and productive relationship between the team and the client.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: Intimacy is exceptionally high. The Product Owner sets an exceptional standard for the ability to efficiently manage communication and leadership, creating a deeply connected and highly collaborative work environment.\",\n  \"The score is out of range or not a number\"\n)",
