        },
        {
          "type": "formula",
          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "SWITCH(\n  {fldvEzA7JIqKjTr0A},\n  1, \"Poor: The Product Owner shows a total lack of ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, as well as to collaborate with clients in defining objectives. Communication is opaque and dishonest.\",\n  2, \"Very Low: The Product Owner has minimal ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and shows minimal collaboration with clients in defining objectives. Communication is very limited and not transparent.\",\n  3, \"Low: The Product Owner shows some ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, albeit limited, and collaborates minimally with clients in defining objectives. Communication is unclear and not honest.\",\n  4, \"Below Average: Although the Product Owner has some ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, as well as to collaborate with clients in defining objectives, their performance falls short of expectations. Communication can be ambiguous and not transparent at times.\",\n  5, \"Average: The Product Owner shows a moderate ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and collaborates acceptably with clients in defining objectives. Communication is mostly clear and honest, although it could improve in some aspects.\",\n  6, \"Satisfactory: The Product Owner has a good ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and collaborates effectively with clients in defining objectives. Communication is generally clear and honest.\",\n  7, \"Moderately High: The Product Owner shows a solid ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and collaborates prominently with clients in defining objectives. Communication is transparent and honest in most cases.\",\n  8, \"High: The Product Owner has an excellent ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and collaborates exceptionally with clients in defining objectives. Communication is clear, transparent, and honest at all times.\",\n  9, \"Very High: The Product Owner shows an exceptional ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and collaborates exceptionally with clients in defining objectives. Communication is extremely transparent and honest.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: The Product Owner demonstrates an exceptionally high ability to understand and communicate the project's needs, and collaborates exceptionally with clients in defining objectives. Communication is impeccably clear, transparent, and honest in all interactions.\"\n)",
