          "type": "formula",
          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "SWITCH(\n  {fldxGggBXt6BQkvHQ},\n  1, \"Poor: The Product Owner fails to effectively plan or distribute project phases and resources, and cannot adapt to sudden changes while maintaining clear and stable direction.\",\n  2, \"Very Low: The Product Owner's ability to plan and distribute project phases and resources is extremely limited, and struggles to adapt to sudden changes.\",\n  3, \"Low: The Product Owner has difficulty effectively planning and distributing project phases and resources, and shows limited adaptation to sudden changes.\",\n  4, \"Below Average: The Product Owner's ability to effectively plan and distribute project phases and resources is slightly below average, and shows some capacity to adapt to sudden changes.\",\n  5, \"Average: The Product Owner has an average ability to plan and distribute project phases and resources, and can adequately adapt to sudden changes while maintaining clear and stable direction.\",\n  6, \"Satisfactory: The Product Owner demonstrates a satisfactory ability to plan and distribute project phases and resources, and can reasonably adapt to sudden changes.\",\n  7, \"Moderately High: The Product Owner's ability to effectively plan and distribute project phases and resources is notably good, and can successfully adapt to sudden changes while maintaining clear and stable direction.\",\n  8, \"High: The Product Owner demonstrates a high ability to plan and distribute project phases and resources effectively, and is very skilled at adapting to sudden changes while maintaining clear and stable direction.\",\n  9, \"Very High: The Product Owner's ability to effectively plan and distribute project phases and resources is exceptionally high, and their ability to adapt to sudden changes is remarkable.\",\n  10, \"Exceptional: The Product Owner exhibits an exceptional ability to effectively plan and distribute project phases and resources, and is extraordinarily adept at adapting to sudden changes while maintaining clear and stable direction.\"\n)",
