        {
          "type": "formula",
          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "SWITCH(\n  {fldxdSG6moz6bwRKO},\n  1, \"Poor: The Product Owner does not promote a collaborative or trusting environment, and fails to establish effective communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, resulting in a total lack of harmony and understanding both within the team and with clients.\",\n  2, \"Very Low: The Product Owner demonstrates minimal ability to promote a collaborative and trusting environment, and communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts are extremely limited, hindering effective problem resolution.\",\n  3, \"Low: Although the Product Owner attempts to promote a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes some communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, their performance is insufficient and does not create a true sense of connection.\",\n  4, \"Below Average: The Product Owner makes efforts to promote a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes some communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, but their effectiveness is limited and there is still much room for improvement.\",\n  5, \"Average: The Product Owner promotes to some extent a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes some communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, with mixed results reflecting an intermediate situation.\",\n  6, \"Satisfactory: The Product Owner effectively promotes a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes adequate communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, contributing positively to the team's functioning and relationships with clients.\",\n  7, \"Moderately High: The Product Owner actively promotes a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes solid communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, creating a positive and productive work atmosphere both within the team and with clients.\",\n  8, \"High: The Product Owner prominently promotes a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes effective and open communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, fostering strong relationships and greater efficiency in work.\",\n  9, \"Very High: The Product Owner demonstrates exceptional ability to promote a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes exceptionally effective communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, creating deep relationships and a highly productive work atmosphere.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: The Product Owner goes above and beyond in promoting a collaborative and trusting environment, and establishes impeccable communication channels to resolve conflicts or doubts, creating exceptional relationships and an exemplary work culture.\"\n)",
