hinking is very high. The client demonstrates exceptional openness to collaborate and receive value propositions, and actively and proactively engages in discussions to enhance the project's success, acting as a catalyst for advancement.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: Group thinking is outstanding. The client displays exceptionally high openness to collaborate and receive value propositions, and participates exceptionally in discussions to enhance the project's success, leading and motivating the team towards excellence.\"\n)",
