            "formula": "SWITCH(\n  {fldK1EWNufaDzTnNs},\n  1, \"Poor: QA shows a complete lack of consistency in meeting deadlines and providing timely responses, with frequent delays and inconsistent or absent responses.\",\n  2, \"Very Low: QA demonstrates very limited consistency in meeting deadlines and providing timely responses, with habitual delays and unreliable responses.\",\n  3, \"Low: QA exhibits unsatisfactory consistency in meeting deadlines and providing timely responses, with frequent delays and unreliable responses.\",\n  4, \"Below Average: QA shows some consistency in meeting deadlines, but often provides late or untimely responses to assigned tasks.\",\n  5, \"Average: QA meets the established deadlines in most cases and provides generally timely responses to assigned tasks, although occasional delays may occur.\",\n  6, \"Satisfactory: QA is consistent in meeting deadlines and provides timely responses to assigned tasks in most cases, with minimal delays.\",\n  7, \"Moderately High: QA demonstrates notable consistency in meeting deadlines and providing timely responses, with infrequent and minimal delays.\",\n  8, \"High: QA shows high consistency in meeting deadlines and providing timely responses, with very infrequent delays.\",\n  9, \"Very High: QA is extremely consistent in meeting deadlines and provides exceptionally timely responses, with virtually no delays.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: QA demonstrates exceptional consistency in meeting deadlines and provides outstandingly timely responses, without delays and with exceptional precision and reliability.\"\n)",
