gh: The Scrum Master is highly reliable in monitoring deadlines, maintaining consistent progress, managing approval processes, and maintaining quality standards at all stages of the project.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: The Scrum Master's ability to perform all these tasks is exceptional, demonstrating extraordinary reliability and serving as a reference model in their work environment.\"\n)",
