tions.\",\n  10, \"Outstanding: The Scrum Master's ability to create an atmosphere of trust and openness within the team is exceptional. An extraordinary level of intimacy is established where members feel completely safe sharing ideas and concerns, promoting collaboration and innovation exceptionally.\"\n)",
