          "options": {
            "isValid": true,
            "formula": "IF(\n  SEARCH(\"Client\", ARRAYJOIN({fldmRzsE2px8vvq83}, \",\")), \n  BLANK(), \n  SWITCH(\n    {fldAybrrcfJM102Wm},\n    1, \"The talent frequently demonstrates poor understanding and pronunciation of English, leading to significant communication issues.\",\n    2, \"The talent often struggles with understanding and pronouncing English, causing frequent misunderstandings.\",\n    3, \"The talent occasionally has difficulties with English understanding and pronunciation, impacting communication effectiveness.\",\n    4, \"The talent has a basic understanding of English, but pronunciation inconsistencies affect clarity.\",\n    5, \"The talent generally understands English well, but occasional pronunciation errors can cause minor communication gaps.\",\n    6, \"The talent is proficient in understanding English and communicates clearly, though some pronunciation nuances could improve.\",\n    7, \"The talent consistently understands and pronounces English accurately, facilitating effective communication.\",\n    8, \"The talent has a strong command of English understanding and pronunciation, enhancing communication within the team.\",\n    9, \"The talent demonstrates excellent understanding and pronunciation of English, ensuring clear and effective communication.\",\n    10, \"The talent is a model of English proficiency, with exceptional understanding and pronunciation, ensuring flawless communication.\",\n    BLANK()\n  )\n)",
